{
  "stem": "9995.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I took all my books, and my mother's friends had a lot of books.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so I had plenty of reading because libraries, everything, of course, were closed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so I didn't feel that I completely-- at that time, I believed that the war will end soon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they closed the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw that my uncle was doing extremely well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was still making very good money, and he could stay in German section of the city in his apartment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- and my mother suggested also to me, since her friend was a teacher in the school where they were learning dressmaking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went, and few other girls also went to her, and I learned how to do the patterns and how to sew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very good at that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My uncle was permitting me to use one of his machine in his place so I could practice this besides doing it in that teacher's house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this gave me certain occupation and feeling that I'm doing something with myself and that I learned something useful, and I enjoy this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't move, as I said, not from grandfather's house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From grandfather's house, we went to the suburbs, where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And over there, I also-- since they were catching people on the street and taking them to work in Germany, there was not enough hands to do.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was working in the field.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was also [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] taking care of the chickens and geese.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also I was milking the cows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I learned to do this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in a way, I really enjoyed that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, it-- it gave me something to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
